{"tid":1161882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登釣魚台","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:54:46.000Z","uid":176508,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9550aa2c2b1acbfcaf4e40a182a84af71a4a789e","tid":1161882,"uid":176508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:16:01.000Z","msg":"希望可以召集喜歡釣魚既巴絲<br />\n本人現以有兩個釣魚群組<br />\n<br />\n一個初學分享基本知識<br />\n一個由2015年已經開左既約釣步兵至遠佂<br />\n<br />\n開post 目的係 因為香港而加周圍都好多人 假日已經唔想街 不如將自己既興趣分享下 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎有興趣由零開始既巴絲一齊玩<br />\n<br />\n我唔一個叻既釣魚人 但係正常分享解答應該應付到<br />\n<br />\n歡迎留低TG 不論男女 我都會盡力講解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8tN6dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8tN6dD.png&h=c057640d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tOiitrZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtOiitrZ.png&h=3a6e1b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvP9z60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvP9z60.png&h=db675e61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nopajyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnopajyH.png&h=934b9967&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqiZcTJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqiZcTJ.png&h=ea93704f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjGDtr3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjGDtr3.png&h=b4879ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftEUMdK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftEUMdK.png&h=99645dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFOBZyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFOBZyL.png&h=51e89383&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3iitr6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3iitr6.png&h=56ff3e96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DS6Thks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDS6Thks.png&h=c9dc6f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OS2fvFW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOS2fvFW.png&h=c2012513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n步兵 到 船釣既小釣獲<br />\n太大我就未試過中<br />\n如果有玩開既巴打 相對都可以對我指教同分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef126e21e020ac6b7486ef7ad23187c157364a9","tid":1161882,"uid":80672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:27:50.000Z","msg":"支持巴打 希望多d人一齊玩"},{"pid":"ce205debfddff4c0ad5d39059c7c1fefc161ca96","tid":1161882,"uid":11614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n師兄係邊度玩前打多？"},{"pid":"ffb4ea056c9a3053100a526926211cc245b5ec5f","tid":1161882,"uid":176508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce205debfddff4c0ad5d39059c7c1fefc161ca96","tid":1161882,"uid":11614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n師兄係邊度玩前打多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"多數都係試橋墩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7859288458b18392bde4afa26611a750da7cf6","tid":1161882,"uid":176508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:19:13.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d844b193dbd0a8a522e89253205ad6c67b591bc2","tid":1161882,"uid":209418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30Ay3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30Ay3n.jpg&h=3f625236&s={SIZE}\" 